# This gitignore is a whitelist. Inspired by https://rgbcu.be/blog/gitignore

*

!.gitignore
!.golangci.yml
!AGENTS.md
!LICENSE.md
!README.md

# Keep root markdown docs explicit so new local notes stay ignored by default.

# Root-level source and docs stay explicit; recursive allowlists are intentional for nested command and test paths.
!*.go
!searchDeciderPrompt.txt
!cmd/
!cmd/**/*
# Keep repo-owned YAML files explicit; local runtime config stays ignored by default.

# Keep runtime and deployment manifests explicit so local-only config files remain ignored.
!Dockerfile
!config-example.yaml
!docker-compose.yaml
!go.mod
!go.sum
!render.yaml
